Package: ess
Title: Download data from the European Social Survey on the fly
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Jorge", "Cimentada", email = "cimentadaj@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The ess package allows you to download data from the European Social Survey. There are two family of functions that allow you to download and interactively check all countries and rounds available from the European Social Survey.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
